\c 25
\s Mapoka evaimbi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi nevakuru vehondo vakatsaurirawo shumiro kuvanakomana vaAsafi nekuna Hemani nekuna Jedhutuni, vanoporofita nembira, nemitengeranwa, nemakandira; neuwandu hwevarume vebasa hwaienderana neshumiro yavo.
\v 2 Kuvanakomana vaAsafi: Zakuri, naJosefa, naNetaniya, naAsarera, vanakomana vaAsafi pasi peruoko rwaAsafi, waiporofita nemurairo wamambo.
\v 3 Kuna Jedhutuni: Vanakomana vaJedhutuni. Gedhariya, naZeri, naJeshaya, Hashabhiya, naMatitiya, vatanhatu pasi peruoko rwababa vavo Jedhutuni waiporofita nembira, kuvonga nekurumbidza Jehovha.
\v 4 KwaHemani: Vanakomana vaHemani; Bhukiya, Mataniya, Uziyeri, Shebhueri, naJerimoti, Hananiya, Hanani, Eriyata, Gidhariti, naRomamitiezeri, Joshibhekasha, Maroti, Hotiri, Mahazioti.
\v 5 Ava vese vanakomana vaHemani, muoni wamambo pamashoko aMwari kusimudza runyanga. Mwari ndokupa kuna Hemani vanakomana gumi nevana, nevakunda vatatu.
\v 6 Ava vese vaiva muruoko rwababa vavo pakuimba muimba yaJehovha, nemakandira, nemitengeranwa, nembira, pashumiro yeimba yaMwari pasi peruoko rwamambo, naAsafi, naJedhutuni, naHemani.
\v 7 Zvino uwandu hwavo pamwe nehama dzavo vaiva vakadzidziswa zvenziyo dzaJehovha, vese vaiva neruzivo hwaiva mazana maviri nemakumi masere nevasere.
\p
\v 8 Zvino vakakanda mijenya basa \add nebasa\add*, mukuru semukuru, mudzidzisi semudzidzi.
\v 9 Zvino mujenya wekutanga wakabudira Asafi kunaJosefa; wepiri Gedhariya; iye nevanin'ina vake nevanakomana vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 10 wetatu kuna Zakuri, vanakomana vake, nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 11 wechina kuna Iziri, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 12 weshanu kuna Netaniya, nevanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 13 wetanhatu kuna Bhukiya, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 14 wechinomwe kuna Jesharera, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 15 wesere kuna Jeshaya, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 16 wepfumbamwe kuna Mataniya, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 17 wegumi kuna Shimei, nevanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 18 wegumi neumwe kuna Azareeri, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 19 wegumi nevaviri kuna Hashabhiya, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 20 wegumi nevatatu kuna Shubhayeri, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 21 wegumi nena kuna Matitiya, vanakomana vake, nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 22 wegumi neshanu kuna Jeremoti, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 23 wegumi netanhatu kuna Hananiya, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 24 wegumi nenomwe kuna Joshibhekasha, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 25 wegumi nesere kuna Hanani, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 26 wegumi nepfumbamwe kuna Maroti, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 27 wemakumi maviri kuna Eriyati, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 28 wemakumi maviri neumwe kuna Hotiri, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 29 wemakumi maviri nevaviri kuna Gidhariti, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 30 wemakumi maviri nevatatu kuna Mahaziyoti, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri;
\v 31 wemakumi maviri nena kuna Romamiti-Ezeri, vanakomana vake nevanin'ina vake, gumi nevaviri.
